      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">53.213</ph> Simplified acquisition
procedures (SF’s 18, 30, 44, 1165, 1449, and OF’s 336, 347, and
348).</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The following forms are prescribed as stated in this
section for use in simplified acquisition procedures, orders under
existing contracts or agreements, and orders from required sources
of supplies and services:</p>
         <ol id="d3778e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3824e12" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/request-quotations"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> SF 18</xref> (Rev.6/95),
Request for Quotations, or <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">SF 1449</xref> (<ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">Rev. <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>Nov <?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 53.213 by—
a. In paragraph (a):
i. Removing the date “( Rev. 2/2012 )” and adding in its place “( Rev. NOV 2021 )”; and 
ii. Removing the words “ Commercial Items” and adding “ Commercial Products and Commercial Services” in their place; and?>2021</ph>), Solicitation/Contract/Order
for <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">Commercial Products
and Commercial Services.</ph>
                  </i>
                  <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/request-quotations"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 18</xref> is
prescribed for use in obtaining price, cost, delivery, and related
information from suppliers as specified in <xref href="13.307.dita#FAR_13_307"
                        base="i1111767"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.307</xref>(b). <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1449</xref>,
as prescribed in <xref href="53.212.dita#FAR_53_212"
                        base="i1001014"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">53.212</xref>, or other agency
forms/automated formats, may also be used to obtain price, cost,
delivery, and related information from suppliers as specified in <xref href="13.307.dita#FAR_13_307"
                        base="i1111767"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.307</xref>(b).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3824e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/amendment-solicitationmodification-contract"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> SF 30</xref> (Rev.11/2016),
Amendment of Solicitation/ Modification of Contract</i>. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/amendment-solicitationmodification-contract"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 30</xref>, prescribed
in <xref href="53.243.dita#FAR_53_243"
                        base="i1001738"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">53.243</xref>, may be used for
modifying purchase orders, as specified in <xref href="13.307.dita#FAR_13_307"
                        base="i1111767"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.307</xref>(c)(3).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3824e65" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/us-government-purchase-order-invoice-voucher"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> SF 44</xref> (Rev.10/83),
Purchase Order Invoice Voucher</i>. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/us-government-purchase-order-invoice-voucher"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 44</xref> is
prescribed for use in simplified acquisition procedures, as specified
in <xref href="13.306.dita#FAR_13_306"
                        base="i1111753"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.306</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3824e80" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/receipt-cash-subvoucher"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> SF 1165</xref> (6/83Ed.),
Receipt for Cash-Subvoucher</i>. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/receipt-cash-subvoucher"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1165</xref> (GAO)
may be used for imprest fund purchases, as specified in <xref href="13.307.dita#FAR_13_307"
                        base="i1111767"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.307</xref>(e).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3824e95" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/continuation-sheet"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> OF 336</xref> (4/86Ed.),
Continuation Sheet</i>. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/continuation-sheet"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">OF 336</xref>, prescribed
in <xref href="53.214.dita#FAR_53_214"
                        base="i1001144"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">53.214</xref>(h), may be used
as a continuation sheet in solicitations, as specified in <xref href="13.307.dita#FAR_13_307"
                        base="i1111767"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">13.307</xref>(c)(1).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3824e113" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1449</xref>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">(<ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">Rev. <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>Nov <?FM MARKER [Why] b. In paragraph (f):
