                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i "> Solicitation/Contract/Order
for <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">Commercial Products
and Commercial Services</ph>
                  </i> prescribed in <xref href="53.212.dita#FAR_53_212"
                        base="i1001014"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">53.212</xref>, <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-0"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">OF 347</xref> (Rev.2/2012),
Order for Supplies or Services, and <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-schedule-continuation"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">OF 348</xref> (Rev.4/06),
Order for Supplies or Services-Schedule Continuation. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1449</xref>,
OF’s <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-0"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">347</xref> and <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-schedule-continuation"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">348</xref> (or approved agency
forms/automated formats) may be used as follows:</p>
               <ol id="d3778e175" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3824e153" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> To accomplish
acquisitions under simplified acquisition procedures, as specified
in <xref href="13.307.dita#FAR_13_307"
                              base="i1111767"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.307</xref>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3824e161" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> To establish
blanket purchase agreements (BPA’s), as specified in <xref href="13.303-2.dita#FAR_13_303_2"
                              base="i1111600"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.303-2</xref>, and to make
purchases under BPA’s, as specified in <xref href="13.303-5.dita#FAR_13_303_5"
                              base="i1111666"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">13.303-5</xref>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3824e172" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> To issue
orders under basic ordering agreements, as specified in <xref href="16.703.dita#FAR_16_703"
                              base="i1103595"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.703</xref>(d)(2)(i).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3824e180" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph> As otherwise
specified in this chapter (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.,</i> see <xref href="5.503.dita#FAR_5_503"
                              base="i1120417"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.503</xref>(a)(2), <xref href="8.406-1.dita#FAR_8_406_1"
                              base="i1117942"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8.406-1</xref>, <xref href="36.701.dita#FAR_36_701"
                              base="i1078213"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">36.701</xref>(b), and <xref href="51.102.dita#FAR_51_102"
                              base="i1066350"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">51.102</xref>(e)(3)(ii)).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
